TI  - Multidisciplinary approach to sediment connectivity between debris-flow channel network and the Dolra River, Mazeri Valley, Southern Caucasus, Georgia
T2  - GEOMORPHOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Sediment connectivity
KW  - Dendrogeomorphology
KW  - Debris flow
KW  - Caucasus Mountains
