TI  - Post-wildfire riparian forest recovery processes along a regulated river corridor
T2  - FOREST ECOLOGY AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Riparian forest
KW  - Seedling recruitment
KW  - Riparian wildfire
KW  - Sediment supply
KW  - Floodplains
