TI  - The Effect of Grain Size on Rainfall-Triggered Debris Flow in Hydrophobic Granular Slopes
T2  - GEO-CONGRESS 2022: GEOENVIRONMENTAL ENGINEERING; UNSATURATED SOILS; AND CONTEMPORARY TOPICS IN EROSION, SUSTAINABLITY, AND COAL COMBUSTION RESIDUALS
