TI  - An intensive tree-ring experience: Connecting education and research during the 25th European Dendroecological Fieldweek (Asturias, Spain)
T2  - DENDROCHRONOLOGIA
LA  - English
KW  - Dendrochronology
KW  - Dendroarchaeology
KW  - Dendroclimatology
KW  - Dendroecology
KW  - Dendrogeomorphology
KW  - Plant anatomy
KW  - GROWTH
KW  - DROUGHT
KW  - CLIMATE
