TI  - Stratigraphic reconstruction of two debris avalanche deposits at Colima Volcano (Mexico): Insights into pre-failure conditions and climate influence
T2  - JOURNAL OF VOLCANOLOGY AND GEOTHERMAL RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - PYROCLASTIC DENSITY CURRENTS
KW  - MOUNT-RAINIER
KW  - COMPLEX
KW  - BEHAVIOR
KW  - TECTONICS
KW  - COLLAPSES
KW  - ERUPTION
KW  - ISLAND
