TI  - Sedimentary facies and evolution of a Mediterranean-type slope-basin in the Early Carboniferous of the Vosges Mountains (Oderen Group, NE-France)
T2  - ZEITSCHRIFT DER DEUTSCHEN GESELLSCHAFT FUR GEOWISSENSCHAFTEN
LA  - English
KW  - Southern Vosges
KW  - Variscides
KW  - Lower Carboniferous
